OL,3,CWood panelling firm fined #400,000
OL,4,Cafter injured worker loses leg
OL,6,FA wood panel manufacturer has been
OL,7,Ffined #400,000 after a worker suffered
OL,8,Flife-changing injuries at its factory
OL,9,Fin Chirk, near Wrexham.
OL,11,FMark Hughes, an employee at Kronospan
OL,12,FLimited, was working at the site on 31
OL,13,FMarch 2021 when a pack of waste MDF
OL,14,Fsheets weighing around 350kg fell from
OL,15,Fa trailer and landed on his left leg.
OL,17,FMr Hughes, now 53, from Johnstown,
OL,18,Fsuffered injuries so severe they
OL,19,Fresulted in him having his left leg
OL,20,Famputated below his knee.
