OL,6,FThe life-changing injury has resulted
OL,7,Fin Mr Hughes having to move to an
OL,8,Faccessible house, and he is no longer
OL,9,Fable to carry on with his hobbies and
OL,10,Fstruggles to climb stairs.
OL,12,F"My injury has changed everything in
OL,13,Fmy life, it is like somebody dropped a
OL,14,Fbomb on our life and never picked up
OL,15,Fthe pieces," he said.
OL,17,F"Everything now just takes a lot of
OL,18,Fplanning to do and spontaneous trips
OL,19,Fdo not happen anymore.
