OL,6,F"I won't go anywhere that has a lot of
OL,7,Fsteps."
OL,9,FAfter more than two years off work, Mr
OL,10,FHughes has returned to the company in
OL,11,Fa part-time capacity.
OL,13,F"Some days I feel okay but some days
OL,14,Fafter work I feel absolutely
OL,15,Fknackered," he said.
OL,17,F"I've worked for Kronospan for 27
OL,18,Fyears and I feel since my accident it
OL,19,Fwould be difficult to find a job
OL,20,Fsomewhere else and start over.
