OL,6,FWhen he began to remove the straps
OL,7,Fholding the sheets in place, a pack
OL,8,Ffell off the trailer and landed on top
OL,9,Fof him. The road across the site was
OL,10,Fpoorly maintained and had lots of
OL,11,Fpotholes, the investigation found.
OL,13,FIt also found that there was no
OL,14,Fsuitable risk assessment or system of
OL,15,Fwork in place specifically relating to
OL,16,Fthe risks associated with the
OL,17,Fstacking, movement and loading of
OL,18,Fwaste MDF sheets.
