OL,3,CWood panelling firm fined #400,000
OL,4,Cafter injured worker loses leg
OL,6,FKronospan Limited of Chirk, Wrexham,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to breaching Section
OL,8,F2(1) of the Health & Safety at Work
OL,9,Fetc. Act 1974.
OL,11,FIt was fined #400,000 and ordered to
OL,12,Fpay costs of #4,701 at Wrexham
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on 19 November 2024.
OL,15,FSpeaking after the hearing, HSE
OL,16,Finspector Marie Wheeler said: "A man
OL,17,Fhas suffered truly life-changing
OL,18,Finjuries as a result of this company's
OL,19,Ffailures.
