OL,6,F"The incident was completely
OL,7,Fpreventable had a proper risk
OL,8,Fassessment been carried out. Nor did
OL,9,Fthe company have a suitable safe
OL,10,Fsystem of work in place.
OL,12,F"HSE will always take action when
OL,13,Fbasic failures like these result in
OL,14,Fvery serious injury."
OL,16,FA spokesperson from Kronospan Ltd
OL,17,Fsaid: "Kronospan Ltd deeply regrets
OL,18,Fthe incident on 31 March 2021 and the
OL,19,Fserious injuries sustained by a long
OL,20,Fstanding and valued employee.
